-- Turkey Alternatifbank's CEO to step down this week -statement 
-- By Matt Smith
-- Wed Mar 26, 2014 02:41AM EDT
-- None



DUBAI, March 26 (Reuters) - The chief executive of Turkey's Alternatifbank <ALNTF.IS>, Hamit Aydogan, will leave his job on March 28, parent firm Commercial Bank of Qatar <COMB.QA> said in a statement to Doha's bourse on Wednesday.

Aydogan was also general manager, the statement said. It added that Muzaffer Ozturk, executive vice-president and head of business, would now become interim general manager.